headline: How supplier collaboration, investing in data can help brands’ EPR transition
summary: At Pack Expo International, key voices involved in EPR scale-up, representing Ameripen, Circular Action Alliance and major brands, sought to educate big crowds about what brands need to know and how suppliers can help.
